{
  "stem": "19518.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 369.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was beaten more by the Jews than I was beaten by Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this went on for about two weeks, three weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not even think about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no answer to it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had no-- I had no reasonable answer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't even ask that question.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I guess they wanted to survive on my back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wanted to survive too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because many of them did not survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many did not survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of them didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the pity of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The head of the police and his wife in Plaszow, they were killed by the Nazi-- by Mr.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Goeth, who was the-- who was the head of the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not in my time, I was already in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But just before the second transport came to Auschwitz, they had a bad end.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And many of their policeman went with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Madritch opened up his factory, and we settled in a life, a routine life, more or less.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Winter in Poland is very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Between snow, and rain, and drizzle, and not having proper clothes, and not having proper shoes, it was not an easy winter at all.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had no water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From my barrack to the latrine, I could not go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because you see, I could have been shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if I opened up the door in the back and took a little bit of snow, I was able to get washed before the flood light went my way.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we used to keep vigil about the flood light and sneak out, and sneak, and get washed quickly whichever way we could, and get dressed for work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when I had the night shift, there was not such a problem, because it was mingling with people.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
